## Setup libraries

Install the following libraries, allways use @latest and pnpm to make sure you are pulling the latest version.

Dependencies:

- threejs
- @react-three/drei
- @react-three/fiber

Dev-dependencies:

- @types/three

## Setup starter scene

If the user asks to create a scene setup, you can use the followign tempalte:

```tsx
"use client";

import { Canvas } from "@react-three/fiber";

export default function Home() {
  return (
    <div className="w-full h-screen relative">
      <Canvas>
        <Scene />
      </Canvas>
    </div>
  );
}

function Scene() {
  return null;
}
```
